<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    table, td, th {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }

    table {
      border-collapse: collapse;
      width: 80%;
    }

    td {
      padding: 15px;
    }

    .table_padding td {
      padding: 12px;
    }

    tr:nth-child(even){background-color: #f2f2f2}
  </style>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />

</head>
<body>
<div class="container" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 35px">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1><span style="color: #A9CC2D; ">Welcome to Cloud Connect</span><small>, <%= @email %></small></h1>
  </div>
  <div class="container" style="margin-top: 30px">
    <div class="row" >
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "logomail.png", width:"400px",style: "padding-top: 18px;" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container" style="margin-top: 10px;">
    <h3>Using the calculator you have chosen the following items for CloudConnect service:</h3>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <table class="table_padding">
          <tr>
            <td >User type</td>
            <td ><%= @veeam_user %></td>
            <td align="right"><% unless @veeam_user_price.to_i <= 0 %><%= number_to_currency(@veeam_user_price, :unit => "" ) %><% end %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td >SERVICE:</td>
            <td ><%= @service %></td>
            <td align="right"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td >PLATFORM:</td>
            <td ><%= @platform %></td>
            <td align="right"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td >BASIC PACKAGE:</td>
            <td ><%= @basic_pack %></td>
            <td align="right"><%= number_to_currency(@service_price, :unit => "" ) %></td>
          </tr>
          <% unless @extra_vm.empty? %>
              <tr>
                <td >ADDITIONAL VM:</td>
                <td ><%= @extra_vm %></td>
                <td align="right"><%= number_to_currency(@extra_vm_price, :unit => "" ) %></td>
              </tr>
          <% end %>
          <% unless @extra_storage.empty? %>
              <tr>
                <td >ADDITONAL STRAGE:</td>
                <td ><%= @extra_storage.to_i/100 %>x100 GB</td>
                <td align="right"><%= number_to_currency(@extra_storage_price, :unit => "" ) %></td>
              </tr>
          <% end%>
          <tr>
            <td ></td>
            <td></td>
            <td align="right" ><b><%= number_to_currency(@sum_price, :unit => "", ) %></b></td>
            <td><b>EUR/month</b></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <h4>The price includes <%= @sum_vm %> VM and <%= @sum_storage %> GB.</h4>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <p>Price is expressed in EURO.</br>
          For users in Croatia price is calculated in kunas according to the selling rate of RBA on the date of invoice.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h4>Use our online calculator. Register and you'll be able to use the calculator  online!</h4>
  </div>
  <hr>
  <h4  style="margin-top: 10px"><span style="color: #A9CC2D; ">Cloud Connect</span> - ba an <span style="color: #A9CC2D; ">„Always On”</span> company!</h4>
</div>

</body>
</html>